{"tid":2408382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人電話騷擾 可以點做","createTime":"2021-02-15T01:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:08:50.000Z","uid":188028,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"79b870e26b24922281075934c50f5e91c2767275","tid":2408382,"uid":188028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T01:29:28.000Z","msg":"由幾日前開始就不停有No caller 打黎<br />\n一開始都有聽 聽完對方就收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後一直唔聽就不停打黎<br />\n係apple set 左silence call之後佢就轉用WhatsApp audio call<br />\n基本上係見一個block 一個<br />\n但佢不停轉唔同電話打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由朝打到晚 由幾個到十幾個到幾十個<br />\n試過放低左電話一陣返黎就變左40個call<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVoice mail box都比佢塞爆左<br />\n目前已經block 左佢大概17個號碼<br />\n佢都有試過signal message 過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔聽電話依家佢會有時夾埋WhatsApp message 黎<br />\n好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下面多圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gp8FvKM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGp8FvKM.png&h=8f73b11c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8N7aKN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8N7aKN.png&h=b796d6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFbsaKO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFbsaKO.png&h=edad33e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hjg7Vbu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjg7Vbu.png&h=11dbf2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftyBOwu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftyBOwu.png&h=0e7518c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e87c2fa75b0da2981325856cb2ea7